A clean, responsive, and interactive Kanban board where users can manage tasks through different stages (e.g., To Do, In Progress, Done).

Core Features:

Create, edit, and delete tasks (cards).
Create and reorder columns.
Drag and drop tasks between columns.
Drag and drop columns themselves.
Persist the board state to the browser's local storage.
Tech Stack:

Framework: React (using Vite for a fast and modern setup)
Styling: Tailwind CSS for a professional and utility-first design.
Drag & Drop: @dnd-kit - A modern, accessible, and powerful library for drag and drop.
Icons: react-icons for adding icons easily.
State Management: zustand - A simple, fast, and scalable state management solution.
